!Sample_treatment_protocol_ch1 = For shRNA-induced samples ("plsdox"), media was supplemented with doxycycline-hyclate (Dox) at 1ÂµM/mL (Sigma, D9891) for 5 days prior to RNA extraction.
!Sample_growth_protocol_ch1 = MiaPaCa2 and Tu8902 cell lines were validated by STR profiling and tested negative for mycoplasma infection (Lonza, LT07-701). Cells were maintained at 37ÂºC and under 5% CO2 in DMEM (GIBCO, #11965) supplemented with 10% FBS.
